        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2427109220" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16373096308551407382">I randomly chose <u>The Virtue of Selfishness</u> and got very disappointed by the content. There wasn&apos;t any mention of the benefits of Selfishness and Ayn Rand discussed randomly on every topic and aspect of life.<br/><br/>He was more focused on defending <i>capitalism and an economy based on richness</i>. The book covers ethical issues of his objectivist philosophy and difficult to absorb. <br/><i>It&apos;s kind of a dry book and needs more than a month to finish if you&apos;re into philosophy.</i></span>
  <span id="freeText16373096308551407382" style="display:none">I randomly chose <u>The Virtue of Selfishness</u> and got very disappointed by the content. There wasn't any mention of the benefits of Selfishness and Ayn Rand discussed randomly on every topic and aspect of life.<br /><br />He was more focused on defending <i>capitalism and an economy based on richness</i>. The book covers ethical issues of his objectivist philosophy and difficult to absorb. <br /><i>It's kind of a dry book and needs more than a month to finish if you're into philosophy.</i></span>
