      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/443285-the-virtue-of-selfishness-a-new-concept-of-egoism">Quotes from The Virtue of Sel...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;The man who does not value himself, cannot value anything or anyone.&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
              &mdash;
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/quotes/50739-the-man-who-does-not-value-himself-cannot-value-anything">1136 likes</a>
            </nobr>
            <div class="clear"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;Men who reject the responsibility of thought and reason can only exist as parasites on the thinking of others.&rdquo;</span>
